WEBVTT

00:10.162 --> 00:11.880
But the good news is
I think it's gonna be between us.

00:11.999 --> 00:13.543
Bad news is the best
man is gonna win.

00:13.695 --> 00:15.503
You can't even watch
them for a second!

00:15.591 --> 00:17.119
It's like... Leaving
them with nobody!

00:17.224 --> 00:18.384
Because you're so good with them.

00:18.672 --> 00:19.479
What does your husband do?

00:19.586 --> 00:21.104
I'm not married.

00:21.279 --> 00:22.872
Don is important.

00:23.031 --> 00:24.264
You know, I found that guy.

00:25.520 --> 00:26.455
I'm gonna hard on you,

00:26.527 --> 00:28.271
only because I think
I see you as an

00:28.384 --> 00:29.544
extension of myself.

